                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Other thread WAY out of control... I want this to be a thread of just suggestions of what would make the current charm situation a more acceptable nerf?
<br />
If you wish to state you view on the nerf or have no clue what nerf i am talking about please refer to <a href="http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=5483" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://www.therunes.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=5483</a>
<br />

<br />
With that said...
<br />

<br />
With the current changes in what would make it acceptable to me is if:
<br />

<br />
Charm had a recourse of 5 ticks or until it took melee or nuke DMG where the DAPS was in the charmed state.
<br />

<br />
A WoM upgrade
<br />

<br />
Removal of the Exp penalties...</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
