                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I hate hate hate this change...
<br />

<br />
I would prefer a 1 perent slow then this awful change.
<br />

<br />
I still hate the 1 percent slow idea btw but it is a better solution then what they have.
<br />

<br />
Regardless, if they insist on nerfing us bare min. they have to strip away the xp penalty.  Honestly, today melee equiped high end would pump out close to the dps of the 1/2 dps pet or an unhasted pet.  The difference between the dps of high end melee vrs pet is equalized by the risk.
<br />

<br />
If you can't balance risk/reward then it's a broken solution.  If you are cutting the dps in half you are cutting potential xp in half.  The xp modifier has to go as it's no longer needed.
<br />

<br />
The other change that is way way outdated is the 4 person agro rule.  No offense but that was almost as bad an idea as this 1/2 dps.
<br />

<br />
Anyhow, to sum it up to make it livable(not likeable) by me is:
<br />
1) remove xp penalty for charm if dps is any way altered
<br />
2) change the 1/2 dps to 1 percent slow
<br />

<br />
-clot
<br />
Chanter of Mortalis on VS</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
